Mercury is banking built for startups. I first heard about the company on T=
witter early last year. At the time, Not Boring had about 1,000 readers and=
 $0 revenue, so I stored a mental note away, for a time, one day, maybe, wh=
en this thing would start making money. Then, lo and behold, it did! So I w=
ent to Stripe Atlas to set up an LLC, and who did Stripe recommend first fo=
r banking? You guessed it=E2=80=A6 Mercury [https://email.mg2.substack.com/=
c/eJxFUMluwyAQ_Zpwq8VufODQS3_DYpkkqDZYeNzKf99JfKiEYNDTvC0FhEfrp9_ajux1zXhu4=
