3SINw].=C2=A0
You know how I feel about Stripe. I took their word for it and signed up. I=
=E2=80=99m glad I did. Mercury offers FDIC-insured bank accounts, virtual a=
nd physical debit cards, and 3-click payment flows. It=E2=80=99s designed t=
o be fast and simple. My favorite feature is being able to click to copy my=
 account number, routing number, and bank address, right on the main page. =
Simple but wonderful.=C2=A0
Mercury doesn=E2=80=99t just help companies manage their money, though, it =
helps them raise it. Mercury Raise [https://email.mg2.substack.com/c/eJxFUM=
tqxDAM_Jr1MfiZdQ4-9NLfMLKtZE0TO_jRkr-vd7dQEBJiGI1mPDTccrnMmWsjz2bbdaJJ-FN3b=
